Meet Praise Fowowe at TOSSE 2017!
Praise Fowowe is an unconventional thinker, futurist, a master practitioner of neuro-linguistics programming, an internationally acclaimed sexuality education strategist, family life therapist and Africa’s premier creator and trainer of Family Systems Engineering, a body of knowledge that assists families build systems that supports their happiness.  He is the Principal consultant of Praise Fowowe International and founder of Center for Sex Education and Family Life. With over 15 years’ experience in handling family life issues, he is credited and regarded as the foremost sexuality educator and strategist to have come out of Africa.

Praise believes the problem of the world is an ADULT & the solution to that problem is a CHILD.  He is happily married to Tosin, one of the nation’s finest family finance expert and they are blessed with David and Charis.
